OL,5, Monty Python actor Eric Idle has said  
OL,6, he is still working at the age of 80   
OL,7, for financial reasons.                 
OL,9,FThe comedian, known as Sir Robin       
OL,10,Fthe-not-quite-so-brave-as-Sir-Lancelot 
OL,11,Fin Monty Python And The Holy Grail,    
OL,12,Fsaid he sold his home last year.       
OL,14,FOn X, formerly Twitter, Idle added: "I 
OL,15,Fdon't know why people always assume    
OL,16,Fwe're loaded. Python is a disaster.    
OL,18,F"I never dreamed that at this age the  
OL,19,Fincome streams would tail off so       
OL,20,Fdisastrously."                         
